commit.message: added 205 extra keywords to emojiSynonyms.json / switched out Wade for Fuse.js
Move filtering to one place in common chain. Remove filteredEmojis variable as it is not requried anymore
Add call to value at the end of Lodash chain. Add missing semicolon
Chain lodash call to filter emojis. Drop checking for 0 length of filterFunctions props as every will return true if collection is empty. Rename emoji param to emojis

Add filterFunctions prop allowing user to specify filter functions that are invoked for every emoji before actual rendering making it possible to show only subset of emojis instead of all of them always
Change name of variable from __mounted to _isMounted
Don't call RecyclerView methods in setTimeout call when component is already unmounted
